{"tid":2461744,"cid":37,"subCid":13,"title":"er.... 想自己裝燈","createTime":"2021-03-25T14:07:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T04:06:13.000Z","uid":273006,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"5c8f6b161d1931d91113b2129cac023061e546ed","tid":2461744,"uid":273006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T14:07:25.000Z","msg":"我想問，如果冇任何經驗，係咪唔駛諗自己整？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n裝修完嘅天花燈位：<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcE2ZfEgssTromtrJCxQrg33fkosctc5WmPZsvjJvkz9s?filename=bkSAgKV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbkSAgKV.jpg&h=71a1ace0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我買咗嘅燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />老闆幫我喺牛後面鑽咗兩個窿<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmT4XMLLTKi1njsSfvHoYrQaUDdYn1TWdFS6AKG6Leto3Z?filename=3eqRzwB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3eqRzwB.jpg&h=10f96b59&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"72620e30e304da3a2aa04fc129352e3971a279a4","tid":2461744,"uid":260744,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T14:10:45.000Z","msg":"有冇油壓鑽？冇=完"},{"pid":"f5d5ece2cf3a08972a75bc6a8d92d15f88a6f8b8","tid":2461744,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T14:11:15.000Z","msg":"下led要有空間放隻牛嫁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好少會安起頂<br />\n<br />\n多數做陳列櫃有膠片起面滲光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58b7e544bb804f45b5af44ae15160464e30a163d","tid":2461744,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T14:12:06.000Z","msg":"再轉隆嫁"},{"pid":"4b93252c5fa546787f52d26cd7b744189bc75bb8","tid":2461744,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T14:27:06.000Z","msg":"快、正"},{"pid":"f743113f4ad020cb5640ef1e18dfd0